::Shredder::

Shredder walks out of the Destron base, jumping up and taking off on a random 
flight. His scanner beeps, reporting a maximal signature that was releasing a 
signal. His comm-link was not set to play back Maximal transmissions, but he 
could still detect them.

He changes his course, heading for the Maximal.
